text: He has been my doctor for many years now. Both the doctor and staff are actually very warm and pleasant. He will ask in detail to ensure the right medications are given. Now even after I have moved out of Bishan, I still go back to Anderson Clinic.

The doctor was quite unprofessional. Touched my eye (which had a stye) without washing his hands or wearing gloves.

When i made payment via paynow, the receptionist took my phone away to the back to show the doctor. I just felt like my phone should not have been taken away from me.
Worst private doc ever.. took forever to see 1 patient. Chit-chatting all the way. Really the 1 star rating not fake one. Dont waste ur time here.
